snippet.description:
The wait is worth it ‚ù§Ô∏è‚Äçüî•

#WashiYoWashi in the thunderous voice of Pawan Kalyan üí•

#OG #TheyCallHimOG

Music : Thaman S
Singer - Pawan Kalyan 

Programmed & arranged by - thaman S 
Song Programmed by - Roshan Vishal
NAKODA & Japanese drums - Sivamani 
Additional TAIKOS & Hokkaido drums - - Beyond Sound (T) 
Vocal Supervision - Thaman S & Sujeeth

Recorded by - Thaman S @ Vibe ( HYD )

Mix and Mastered by Shadab Rayeen @ New Edge ( Mumbai )
Assistant engineers - Jazbaat, Sohamm, Prasad

Musicians Co Ordinator - Manikandan K
Studio Manager - Seenu & Sridhar
Studio Assistance - Raju, Kannan, Lingam & Pawan

Cast - Pawan Kalyan, Emraan Hashmi, Priyanka Arul Mohan, Arjun Das, Sriya Reddy, Prakash Raj

Movie Name: They Call Him OG
Written & Directed by Sujeeth
Music by Thaman S
Production: DVV Entertainment
Presented by: Smt D.Parvathi
Produced by DVV Danayya, Kalyan Dasari
Cinematographers : Ravi K Chandran (ISC), Manoj Paramahamsa (ISC)
Production Designer : AS Prakash
Editor: Navin Nooli
Costume Designers: Darshan Jalan & Neelanchal Kumar Ghosh
Action Masters : A Vijay, Peter Hein, Dhilip Subbarayan, Kevin Kumar, Stunt Silva, Sunil Rodrigues, Kecha Khampakdee, Juji, Supreme Sundar, Jashwa, Parvez
Co-director: Somaraju PVV
Direction Department : Uday Alla, Aarun Thevar, Lokesh Srinivasan, Kishore Sarella,
Kedar Pashikanti, Durga D.R, Sainadh Alla, Mithilesh Sivagani, Rithica Devireddy,
I.Chaitanya Sravanth, N.Sruti Ranjani, RSN.Roshan Sharif
Creative Producer : Harish Pai
Chief Associate Editors : Raam tumu, Srinu Bainaboyina
Associate Editors: Prashanth Tej, Yogi (D.F.Tech), Vishnu ramagiri
Executive Producer: Sathyanarayana Guggilla
Production Controller: Manikanta Rongala
Sound Design : Sync Cinema
VFX Supervisor : Raghav Tammareddy
Stills : Mallesh Thatha
Creative Director : Ashwin Mani
Marketing: Walls and Trends
PRO: Venugopal
DI : Annapurna Studios
Marketing : Walls & Trends
Video composition: Walls & Trends

Lyrics -
WASHI YO WASHI 
EAGLE OH EAGLE 

Yasei no washi o korosu ni wa 
To kill a wild Eagle 

Mazu tsubasa o kiri otosu hitsu yoo ga aru 
You need to cut its wings first 

Jimen ni ochitara..me o eguri dasu 
When it falls on the ground you pluck its eyes 

Me ga mienaku nari, doko ni ikeba ii no ka wakara naku suru 
It becomes blind and doesn‚Äôt know where to go 

Sokode ashi o kitte ugokenaku suru 
That‚Äôs when you cut its legs and make it immobile 

Soshite, yasei no shinzou o eguri dasu noda 
And that‚Äôs when you will pluck its wild heart out 

WASHI YO WASHI 
EAGLE O EAGLE

snippet.description:
KRAMP Teaser on Hasya Movies.

KRAMP is an Upcoming 2025 Telugu Movie Starring Kiran Abbavaraam, Yukti Thareja & Others. Directed by Jains Nani. Music by Chaitan Bharadwaj. snippet.description:

You so perfect! üíØ

Dharma Productions & Mentor Disciple Entertainment present 
A Dharma Productions Film
Starring Varun Dhawan, Janhvi Kapoor, Sanya Malhotra, & Rohit Saraf

Produced by Hiroo Yash Johar, Karan Johar, Adar Poonawalla, Apoorva Mehta & Shashank Khaitan

Written by Shashank Khaitan
Dialogues by Shashank Khaitan & Ishita Moitra

Lyrics:

Sir to pairan de takk
You r so perfect
Pind to shehran de takk
You r so perfect

Kim to v gol lakk
Because You r so perfect
Saare te Tere te jatonde hakk
Because You r so perfect

Sohniye bullan di teri surkhi
Tu patt dita turki
Gall teri turpi

Haye Heer ne a diti tenu gudti
Ni fit Teri kurti
Lata di jiwe murki

Agg lone nakhre ne Patt ta punjab ni
Tuhi kalli dunia te kutt di swaad ni
Tere aage lagde husan saare farzi
Na koi tetho pehla sohni na koi tetho baad ni

Gol gol addian di thakk thakk
You r so perfect
Dressa utte laawe lakh
You r so perfect

Matthe ali teri latt
You r so perfect
Teri juye to v maadi latt
Not so Perfect

Lembo vangu vish vish dharti te ture
Tera Dubbel swing lakk khaye ni
London de sab to mashoor darji to
Gale paan patte ale tu rakaye ni

Akhian to shed shed chakk di nai
Lang jawe Mundyea nu takk di nai
Kade LA kade tu dubai huni ae
Kr kr shoppinga tu thakk di nai

Kacrch di lakh lakh
You r so perfect
Nikl di jach jach
You r so perfect
Teri beauty nu number 10
You r so perfect
Chobaran nu pondi gash
No so perfect

Husna da dang maare Naag di bachi
Toba toba agg kudi banke nachi
Naina ch saroor 7 bottela jinna
Reshami jehe aang odi Umar kachi

Guru nu v maare akh
You r so perfect
Gill Rony laye patt
You r so perfect
Pinda de tu maare jatt
You r so perfect
Tenu maaf ne Qatal 8
Not so perfect

You r so perfect
Pind to shehran de takk
You r so perfect

Kim to v gol lakk
Because You r so perfect
Saare te Tere te jatonde hakk
Because You r so perfect

Sohniye bullan di teri surkhi
Tu patt dita turki
Gall teri turpi

Haye Heer ne a diti tenu gudti
Ni fit Teri kurti
Lata di jiwe murki

Agg lone nakhre ne Patt ta punjab ni
Tuhi kalli dunia te kutt di swaad ni
Tere aage lagde husan saare farzi
Na koi tetho pehla sohni na koi tetho baad ni

Gol gol addian di thakk thakk
You r so perfect
Dressa utte laawe lakh
You r so perfect

Matthe ali teri latt
You r so perfect
Teri juye to v maadi latt
Not so Perfect

Lembo vangu vish vish dharti te ture
Tera Dubbel swing lakk khaye ni
London de sab to mashoor darji to
Gale paan patte ale tu rakaye ni

Akhian to shed shed chakk di nai
Lang jawe Mundyea nu takk di nai
Kade LA kade tu dubai huni ae
Kr kr shoppinga tu thakk di nai

Kacrch di lakh lakh
You r so perfect
Nikl di jach jach
You r so perfect
Teri beauty nu number 10
You r so perfect
Chobaran nu pondi gash
No so perfect

Husna da dang maare Naag di bachi
Toba toba agg kudi banke nachi
Naina ch saroor 7 bottela jinna
Reshami jehe aang odi Umar kachi

Guru nu v maare akh
You r so perfect
Gill Rony laye patt
You r so perfect
Pinda de tu maare jatt
You r so perfect
Tenu maaf ne Qatal 8
Not so perfect

Welcome to the World of Vrusshabha.

A unique story brought to life through an unforgettable cinematic experience for global audiences. With Mohanlal playing a king for the very first time in a bilingual epic, Vrusshabha is a film that promises to stay with you long after you leave the theatre. snippet.title: Nallaru Po | Dude | Pradeep Ranganathan | @SaiAbhyankkar | Tippu | Mohit Chauhan | Keerthiswaran
snippet.description:
Presenting the Lyrical Video song of 'Nallaru po' from 'Dude', Written & Directed by Keerthiswaran featuring Pradeep Ranganathan, Mamitha Baiju, R.Sarath Kumar, Hridhu Haroon,Rohini, Aishwarya sharma, Dravid selvam & Others.

An @SaiAbhyankkar  Musical 
Song Title: 'Nallaru po'
Album: Dude

Music Credits:

YOLO Rechords
Music Composed and Produced by @SaiAbhyankkar 
Lyrics: Vivek
Singers : @SaiAbhyankkar , Tippu, Mohit Chauhan
Keys, Synths and Bass: @SaiAbhyankkar 

Music supervisor: 

Chorus Recorded at Sound Town Studios by Rajesh kannan 
Recorded at YOLO Rechords, Engineered by Rajesh Kannan  
Assistants: Sankeerth Shaji, Augustine Premkumar
Mixed by Sai Abhyankkar  
Mastered by Rupendar Venkatesh at Sai 
Dhwani Studios

Producers: Naveen Yerneni, Y Ravi shankar

Colorist: Suresh ravi 
Sound Design: Sync Cinema
Sound Mix: Rajakrishnan M.R
Direction team: Krish Chidambaram, K.C. Perumal, Anirudh Ramesh, Tamilselvan Sankar, Karthick Sekar, Giriprasath, N. Nagaraj
Cinematography team: Yogi Chowdary kotapati, Govinda Rao.P, Dwarak Bharadwaj, Pradeep Raja
Editing Team: Lokesh Raj, Aathieswaran Rajakumar
Art team: Dharma P. Kamalahasan B.F.A, Vaishnavi Ramji, Subiksha Srinivasan, Archana Palani
Stills: M.Dinesh
Publicity Designer:  Viyaki
PRO: Suresh Chandra, Sathish S2Media
Production Controllers : Rangaraj Perumal, E. Suresh Nambiraj
Marketing: First Show
Lyric Video: ADFX


Lyrics:

Nee ketaa unna kooda un kaiyil vittu poguren
Aasa pola vaazhndhukkoyen po
Un mela kaadhal vachene
Thothadhaalum theerala
Ponadhaalum maarala 

Nee ketaa unna kooda un kaiyil vittu poguren
Aasa pola vaazhndhukko di po
Ennalum Kaadhal kuthadhu 
Parvayal Yenga Vechaale 

Paakaama pesaama seraama ponaalum 
Ennaalum nallaru po 
Hey thaangaama thoongaama naan inga vaazhndhaalum
Neeyaachum nallaaru po
 
Kaadhalaa en nenjam
Yekkamaa aanan naane
Kaayamaa nee senjum
Sirikkirene
Yaaradi kutham solla 
En vidhi  enna kolla 
Nee vantha nenjukkulla  
Ippothu onnumilla 

Veroru kayyoda un veral paathen naane 
Vegura nenjoda pogurene
Nethu un kannil naane
Innaikku yaaro dhaane 
Thindaadurene maane
Thaa po nu vittutene 

Paakaama pesaama enkuda seraama ponaalum nallaru po 
Hey thaangaama thoongaama naan inga vaazhndhaalum 
Neeyaachum nallaarupo 

Hey Innoruthanoda nee poga 
Ullolachaloda naan poga 
Enna panna poren Thikku theriyaadhe 
Aanaa neeyum po
 
Hey Ennapanna poren kekaadha
Indha pakkam neeyum paakaadha
Michamulla kaadhal atchadhaya podum 
Nallaa vaazhu po

snippet.title: ANACONDA ‚Äì Official Trailer (HD)
snippet.description:
I like big snakes and I cannot lie. Paul Rudd and Jack Black star in #AnacondaMovie ‚Äì exclusively in theatres Christmas.

Follow Us on Social:
https://x.com/Anaconda_Movie
https://www.facebook.com/AnacondaMovie
https://www.tiktok.com/@anacondamovie
https://www.instagram.com/anacondamovie

Visit our site: https://anacondamovie.com/

Subscribe for more exclusive content: https://www.youtube.com/@sonypictures

Doug (Jack Black) and Griff (Paul Rudd) have been best friends since they were kids, and have always dreamed of remaking their all-time favorite movie: the cinematic "classic" Anaconda. When a midlife crisis pushes them to finally go for it, they head deep into the Amazon to start filming. snippet.title: XLG vs. SEN ‚Äî VALORANT Champions Paris ‚Äî Group Stage
snippet.description:
Welcome to the climax of the 2025 VALORANT Champions Tour! The biggest stage in VALORANT is ready, the lights of Paris are shining, and the countdown has begun. Following a season of historic rivalries, epic comebacks, and unforgettable moments, the world‚Äôs top teams now gather at Champions Paris.

From September 12 to October 5, the journey continues through Group Stage and Playoffs before the epic conclusion at the Grand Final with the crowning of the next World Champion. The Group Stage will feature 16 teams spread across four groups, with each group hosting one team from VALORANT's four International Leagues. In this stage, teams will battle through a double elimination format, advancing two teams out of each group. The 8 teams who make it out will be randomly seeded into a double elimination bracket, with teams from the same group placed on opposite sides of the bracket. Teams will compete through Best-of-3 matches until the final 2 matches which will be a Best-of-5. The last team standing will claim the title of VALORANT World Champion!

We‚Äôre proud to work with our fantastic partners throughout 2025: AWS, Coinbase, EWC, HyperX, Mastercard, OMEN, Red Bull, Secretlab, and Verizon.

Make sure to follow the official VALORANT Esports social channels for additional information:
Twitter/X: @valorantesports

Instagram: @valorantesports
